App requirements:

1. Features of the app will be focusing in the client needs.
2. Platform will be available in Android(google play store) also in Iphone(app store)
3. The app will be built will Java Programming language.
4. We will develop a user interface for the customer to search reserve and manage car rentals. 
5. After that we will take care to develop a server to manage data and perform business logic.
6. One of our staff members will make sure to connect the app to a payment gateway to process transactions.
7. All of us will check the app and thoroughly test the app for functionality, security, and performance.
8. In the end we will launch the app and release it on the app store and make it available for download for any user.
